<div class="container">
  <p class="page-title">About Tico</p>
  <p class="modal__body-text">Tico sets the scene, then plays each guest's line as it happens — you don't need to tap anything to hear them.</p>
  <p class="modal__body-text">When it's your turn, the mic button at the bottom lights up. Tap it and respond the way you actually would on shift — there's no script, so just roll with whatever you're handed.</p>
  <p class="modal__body-text">Tico coaches you along the way and tracks your progress on each sub-skill.</p>
